      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_02-mna001.m4a",
      "text": "自分の全身全霊を込めなきゃ\n誰かの心を動かすことなんて、絶対に出来ない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You have to put your entire being into it‚\notherwise‚ you’ll never be able to move anyone emotionally.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.7333333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 7.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_02-mna002.m4a",
      "text": "あなたが向かい合うのは、琴乃でも私でもない\n――観客よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You shouldn’t be singing for Kotono or for me.\nYou should sing for the audience.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.221483681752131,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_02-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "…………\n全身全霊を……込める",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…\nPut my… entire being into it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.181312165941517,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 19.199047851562508
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "……さくら？\nもしかして、麻奈の声が聞こえるのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Sakura?\nDid you hear Mana’s voice?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.865714518229176,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 23.932381184895814
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_02-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "いえ\nでも、心臓が……なんかドキッとして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No.\nBut my heart… just started pounding.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.365714518229176,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 30.49904785156251
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_02-mna003.m4a",
      "text": "……やっぱり、間違いなく私の心臓なのね……\nだから、私の歌声がさくらちゃんのものになったのか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That definitely is my heart‚ no mistaking it.\nMaybe that’s how Sakura wound up with my voice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.76571451822917,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 40.265714518229196
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ああ\nさくらは心臓の反応に従ってここまで来たんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah.\nSakura‚ you’ve been guided by your heart’s reactions up until now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.266666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 44.89904785156249
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_02-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "はい。そうすると何もかもうまくいったし\n楽しい気持ちになったし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right. Everything’s always worked out well that way.\nAnd it makes me feel happy‚ too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.699047851562504,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 51.199047851562504
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_02-mna004.m4a",
      "text": "……じゃあ、自分の意志でアイドルに\nなりたかった訳じゃ、ないの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then… you didn’t become an idol of\nyour own free will?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.932381184895824,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……麻奈…………",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mana…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.676108838153134,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 57.86769616706396
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_02-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？　麻奈さん、なんて？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? What did Mana say?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.86769616706396,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……アイドルを始めたのは心臓の導きのせいで\n自分の意志じゃなかったのかって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You became an idol only because your heart guided you to do it‚\nnot of your own free will.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.17449888490862,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 67.14251662197934
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_02-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "……最初はそうだったかもしれない\nでも、琴乃ちゃんやみんなと仲間になって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That might have been the case at first‚\nbut after I became friends with Kotono and the others‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.10918328864598,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 74.51742008865934
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_02-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "そして、大きな目標を追いかけるようになって……\n今は、これが私のやりたかったことだって言えます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and after I started chasing after such a big dream…\nI can say now‚ with certainty‚ that this is what I wanted to do.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.21742008865932,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_02-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "だから、麻奈さんの心臓には\nありがとうって思っているんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ Mana‚ I only have feelings of\ngratitude towards your heart.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.084086755326,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 88.35075342199266
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_02-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "私も気付いていなかった\n本当に私がやりたいことを見つけてくれて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for showing me what I really wanted to do\nbut never noticed on my own.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.884086755326,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 94.15075342199266
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "……麻奈。結局、心臓もさくらの一部って\nことなんじゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mana‚ don’t you think this proves your heart is\nalso a part of Sakura?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.68408675532598,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 100.08408675532598
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_02-mna005.m4a",
      "text": "……え？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…It has?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.084086755326,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 101.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈の再来と言われる歌声が出せたり\n心臓の反応で行動を決めたりすることも含めて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It gave Sakura the voice that made others call her your second coming.\nIt helped her make decisions based on its reactions.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "……うまく言えないけど、麻奈の心臓も\n今のさくらを形作る大事なものなんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s hard to explain‚ but… Mana‚ your heart was essential\nin helping shape Sakura into who she is today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 115.16666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_02-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "はい……私もそう思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. I agree.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.16666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_02-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "実は麻奈さんの歌を、本当に私が歌っていいのか\nずっと悩んでいたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To tell the truth‚ I was actually worried all this time that it\nwasn’t really okay for me to sing your song‚ Mana.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_02-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "でも、この心臓が麻奈さんのものだと知って\nはっきり分かりました。私が歌わなきゃって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But now that I know that I have your heart‚\neverything’s clear to me now. I have to sing your song.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 132.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_15_02-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんにも言います。この心臓は麻奈さんの\nものだって。私が責任持ってちゃんと歌うって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And I’m going to tell Kotono. I’m going to tell her I have your heart.\nThat I’ll take responsibility for it and do your song justice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.26666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 140.93333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
